    f.write('## 4. Critical Pitfalls & Warnings\n\n')
    f.write('1. **main.js is ~1970 lines (over 1500 budget).** Any additions to main.js should be minimal. Prefer extracting UI refresh logic to helper functions or the respective module classes.\n\n')
