    f.write('5. **Set bonuses are manufacturer-based, not slot-based.** Adding slots does not break set bonuses, but it makes 4pc easier to achieve. Consider capping set bonuses or adding slot-specific restrictions.\n\n')
    f.write('6. **AffixSystem rollAffixes() takes a slot parameter** but currently does NOT filter by slot. If you want shoulder pads to only roll defense affixes, add slot-based filtering to pickUnique().\n\n')
    f.write('7. **LegendaryPowerSystem reads affixes from a hardcoded slot list in main.js.** If you add slots and want legendary powers from accessories to work, ensure the refresh loop includes them.\n\n')
    f.write('8. **Player.getRPGStats()** delegates to CharacterSheet.getStats(). Any new stats must flow through CharacterSheet._defaultGearBonuses() or they will be dropped during getStats().\n\n')
